OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FThe UK has seen one of its longest
OL,7,Fsummer dry spells for more than 30
OL,8,Fyears, with three heatwaves in three
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FMany parts of England have only had 3%
OL,12,Fof their average July rainfall.
OL,14,FNorth Wales and the Upper Severn
OL,15,Fdeclared drought status on Thursday,
OL,16,Fas dry weather has caused record-low
OL,17,Friver levels.
OL,19,FWildfires blazed across the UK, fueled
OL,20,Fby the hotter, dry conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
