OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784854088
OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FThe big question is when will it rain
OL,7,Fagain and if so where?
OL,9,FHow dry is it?
OL,11,FWith the school holidays close and in
OL,12,Fsome cases already underway, some
OL,13,Fparents may be hoping for a continued
OL,14,Fstreak of good weather.
OL,16,FThe UK is known for its wet summers,
OL,17,Fso it is understandable to question
OL,18,Fwhether the settled dry, sunny and hot
OL,19,Fweather will take a turn at a time
OL,20,Fwhen families want to get outside.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
