OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784854088
OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FThis year, rain is very much needed,
OL,7,Fwith drought being declared in north
OL,8,FWales and hosepipe bans in place for
OL,9,Fmore than 20 million customers.
OL,11,FTechnically, we're only just past the
OL,12,Fmid-way point of the season. For
OL,13,Ffarmers, the rain cannot come soon
OL,14,Fenough.
OL,16,FThe ground is visibly parched, tinder
OL,17,Fdry and straw like - and the risk of
OL,18,Fwildfires remains.
OL,20,FHow long has it been dry?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
