OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FIt's been one of the longest summer
OL,7,Fdry spells in since at 1995.
OL,9,FSome spots in the UK have recorded
OL,10,Fbarely any rain, if at all, throughout
OL,11,FJuly and through the second half of
OL,12,FJune.
OL,14,FThe late June heat triggered some high
OL,15,Frainfall totals in a short space of
OL,16,Ftime as thunderstorms developed.
OL,18,FWithin 24 hours near 30,000 lightning
OL,19,Fstrikes were recorded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
