OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FHowever, parts of southern England
OL,7,Fhave not received any rain for over a
OL,8,Fmonth. In Wisley, Surrey, it has been
OL,9,Fbone dry for seven weeks.JWales has
OL,10,Falso been notably dry since mid-June.
OL,12,FIs it set to rain anytime soon?
OL,14,FThis weekend high pressure, which has
OL,15,Fbeen keeping it settled and dry for
OL,16,Fweeks, gives way as frontal systems
OL,17,Fdrift in from the north.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
