OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FParts of Scotland and Northern
OL,7,FIreland, as well as northern England
OL,8,Fand north Wales, will see some rain,
OL,9,Fmore so in the west.
OL,11,FRainfall totals will not be high but
OL,12,Fwill be welcome. Some areas will see
OL,13,Fmore fall this weekend than over the
OL,14,Flast few weeks.
OL,16,FTemperatures will dip, making things
OL,17,Ffeel a lot cooler.
OL,19,FFurther east and south, any rain will
OL,20,Fbe patchy and hit and miss, but any
OL,21,Famount of rainfall will be appreciated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
