OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FIt will stay hot in the south-east
OL,7,Fbefore a fresher feel into Sunday.
OL,8,FSome areas will escape the dry
OL,9,Fconditions again with spells of
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,12,FFor many it will feel like a different
OL,13,Fweekend compared previous ones.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,20,FHow about next week?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
