OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FInto next week there will be a north-
OL,7,Fsouth split. High pressure is set to
OL,8,Freestablish itself in the south and
OL,9,Fthere will be more late July sunshine.
OL,10,FTemperature will increase once more.
OL,12,FLow pressure to the north will mean
OL,13,Fmore of a breeze and outbreaks of rain
OL,14,F- mostly further west.
OL,16,FIt will feel cooler here too with
OL,17,Flower temperatures like the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
