PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784854088
OL,3,CDrought, heatwaves and hosepipe bans:
OL,4,CWhen and where will it rain?
OL,6,FIt looks like a different theme with
OL,7,Frainfall for the rest of July, with
OL,8,Fmost of the action further north and
OL,9,Fwest.
OL,11,FThe south and south-east will remain
OL,12,Fdrier with more sunshine for many.
OL,14,FHowever we can expect some showery
OL,15,Frain at times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
